======================================================================

vim-instant-markdown (Instant Markdown previews from VIm!)

vim-instant-markdown is a plugin for instant-markdown-d that allows
you to edit a file in VIm and simultaneously see the changes in a 
browser window.
It's works with xdg-utils

HOME: https://github.com/suan/vim-instant-markdown

======================================================================
REQUIRES: instant-markdown-d

